# Title: Remote Thread Creation Via PowerShell
# Author: Nikita Nazarov, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-06
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the creation of a remote thread from a Powershell process to another process
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1059.001, detection.threat-hunting
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-threat-hunting/windows/create_remote_thread/create_remote_thread_win_powershell_generic.yml

SourceImage IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") NOT SourceParentImage="*:\\Windows\\System32\\CompatTelRunner.exe"